I know this post is old, but there's a version of GME that now uses FlasCC / CrossBridge. You can find it at <a href="https://github.com/mcannizz/gme-flascc" class="postlink">https://github.com/mcannizz/gme-flascc</a><br /><br />It uses SWIG and is much faster than the GME Alchemy SWC from <a href="https://code.google.com/p/game-music-emu-flash/" class="postlink">https://code.google.com/p/game-music-emu-flash/</a> assuming that's where you got the SWC from.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=6135">steveswl</a> — Tue Apr 01, 2014 1:35 am</p><hr />
